#To find genes that are differentially expressed in gt 2 & 6 vs 3


```r
dge.fit <- glmFit(dge, design1)
#colnames(dge.fit)
dge.lrt <- glmLRT(dge.fit,coef = c("genotype2","genotype6"))
#the top 10 most differentially expressed genes
topTags(dge.lrt)
```

